data.title: Wikipedia:WikiProject Football/England task force
data.text:
Welcome to the England task force of WikiProject Football.

The England taskforce covers:

All English clubs, leagues and competitions and associated articles

English football organisations

Players and managers that are English, or have played for an English club.

Stadiums in England

Matches played in England

Articles associated with the England National team.

Not to be included

International competitions or matches

Any articles that are within the scope of this project should be tagged with {{Football}}. You should add England = yes as this will automatically put the page in the appropriate categories.

The script at User_talk:Outriggr/metadatatest.js may be useful in tagging and assessing articles.

= {{User WikiProject Football/England task force}}

As of , there are 275 featured articles and lists, and 664 good articles within English football task force scope. This makes up 0.7% of the articles on Wikipedia, 2.5% of all featured articles and lists, and 1.66% of all good articles.
